description: Returns information for a software set.

parameters.name: id
parameters.description: The ID of the software set for which to return information.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the software set.

nested_items.name: version
nested_items.description: The version of the software set.

nested_items.name: releasedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the software set was released.

nested_items.name: supportedUntil
nested_items.description: The timestamp of the end of support for the software set.

nested_items.name: validationStatus
nested_items.description: An option to define if the software set has been validated.

nested_items.name: software
nested_items.description: A list of the software components in the software set.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the software component.

nested_items.name: version
nested_items.description: The version of the software component.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the software set.
